         MACRO                                                          00160000
.*                                                                      00170000
.* Structured programming macro: ENDCASE                                00180000
.* Combines with CASE and ELSE to conditionally execute blocks of code  00190000
.*                                                                      00200000
&LABEL   ENDCASE ,                     * No arguments allowed           00210000
.********************************************************************** 00211001
.*                                                                      00212001
